   You may do so in any reasonable manner, but not in any way that suggests
   the authors endorse you or your use.

2. FREE ACCESS: Community Prompts must remain freely accessible to all users
   of your App. You may NOT:
   - Place Community Prompts behind a Paywall
   - Require payment to access Community Prompts
   - Restrict access to Community Prompts based on subscription tiers
