3. SHARE ALIKE: If you distribute modified versions of the Prompts, you must
   distribute them under this same license.

PERMITTED MONETIZATION

You MAY monetize:
- Services that enhance or process user-created prompts (not Community Prompts)
- Features unrelated to Community Prompts
- Optional donations or tips
